\c 27
\s Imilayo yezithembiso ezithile
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Umuntu, nxa esenza isithembiso esikhethekileyo, njengesilinganiso sakho\x + 27.3,4; 5.15,18; 6.6. Jobe 28.13,17. Hlab. 55.13.\x* imiphefumulo izakuba ngeyeN\nd kosi\x + Nani 6.2. Nani 30. Hlu. 11.30,31,39. 1 Sam. 1.11,28.\x*\nd*.
\v 3 Khona isilinganiso sakho sizakuba ngesowesilisa, kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi ayisithupha, isilinganiso sakho sizakuba \w ngamashekeli\w** esiliva angamatshumi amahlanu, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele\x + 27.25. Eks. 38.24.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa uba kungowesifazana, isilinganiso sakho sizakuba ngamashekeli angamatshumi amathathu.
\v 5 Njalo nxa kusukela koleminyaka emihlanu kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili, isilinganiso sakho sowesilisa sizakuba ngamashekeli angamatshumi amabili, lakowesifazana amashekeli alitshumi.
\v 6 Njalo nxa kusukela kolenyanga kusiya koleminyaka emihlanu, isilinganiso sakho sowesilisa sizakuba ngamashekeli amahlanu esiliva, njalo kowesifazana isilinganiso sakho sizakuba ngamashekeli amathathu esiliva.
\v 7 Uba-ke kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi ayisithupha langaphezulu, uba kungowesilisa, isilinganiso sakho sizakuba ngamashekeli alitshumi lanhlanu, lakowesifazana amashekeli alitshumi.
\v 8 Kodwa uba engumyanga kulesilinganiso sakho, uzazimisa phambi kompristi ukuze umpristi amlinganise; njengalokho\x + 27.16,18; 25.51.\x* isandla sowathembisayo singafinyelela kukho umpristi uzamlinganisa\x + 25.26.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Njalo uba kuyinyamazana abanikela okwayo umnikelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, konke okwayo anikela ngakho eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kuzakuba ngcwele.
\v 10 Kayikuyintshintsha, futhi angenaniseli ngayo, enhle ngembi loba embi ngenhle. Uba-ke usenanisa lokwenanisa inyamazana ngenyamazana, lokhu lalokhukwenaniselana kuzakuba ngcwele.
\v 11 Njalo uba kuyinyamazana loba yiyiphi engcolileyo abanganikeli okwayo ngayo umnikelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uzayimisa inyamazana phambi kompristi,
\v 12 umpristi ayilinganise-ke, ukuthi inhle loba imbi; njengesilinganiso sakho, mpristi, izakuba njalo.
\v 13 Kodwa uba eyihlenga lokuyihlenga, uzakwengezelela ingxenye yesihlanu yayo phezu kwesilinganiso sakho\x + 27.15,19.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Umuntu, nxa engcwelisa-ke indlu yakhe, ukuthi ibe ngcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, umpristi uzayilinganisa, ukuthi inhle loba imbi; njengalokho umpristi ezayilinganisa izakuma njalo.
\v 15 Uba-ke oyingcwelisileyo ezayihlenga indlu yakhe, uzakwengezelela ingxenye yesihlanu yemali yesilinganiso sakho phezu kwayo, njalo izakuba ngeyakhe\x + 27.13.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Uba-ke umuntu ezangcwelisela iN\nd kosi\nd* okwensimu yelifa lakhe, isilinganiso sakho sizakuba njengokwenhlanyelo yayo. \w Ihomeri\w** lenhlanyelo \w yebhali\w** libe ngamashekeli esiliva engamatshumi amahlanu.
\v 17 Uba engcwelisa insimu yakhe kusukela emnyakeni \w wejubili\w**, njengesilinganiso sakho izakuma.
\v 18 Kodwa uba wangcwelisa insimu yakhe emva kwejubili, umpristi uzambalela imali ngokweminyaka eseleyo kuze kufike umnyaka wejubili, njalo kuzaphungulwa esilinganisweni sakho\x + 25.15,16.\x*.
\v 19 Uba-ke owayingcwelisayo eyihlenga lokuyihlenga insimu, uzakwengezelela ingxenye yesihlanu yemali yesilinganiso sakho phezu kwayo, njalo iqiniswe kuye\x + 27.13.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa uba engayihlengi insimu, loba uba eseyithengisile insimu komunye umuntu, kayisayikuhlengwa.
\v 21 Kodwa insimu ekuphumeni kwayo ngejubili izakuba ngcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 25.31.\x*, njengensimu eyehlukanisiweyo\x + 27.28,29.\x*; ilifa layo libe ngelompristi\x + Nani 18.14. Hez. 44.29.\x*.
\v 22 Uba-ke eyingcwelisela iN\nd kosi\nd* insimu ayithengileyo, engayisiyo insimu yelifa lakhe\x + 25.10,25.\x*,
\v 23 umpristi uzambalela-ke\x + 27.18.\x* inani lesilinganiso sakho, kuze kufike umnyaka wejubili, abesenika isilinganiso sakho ngalolosuku, into engcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 12.4.\x*.
\v 24 Ngomnyaka wejubili insimu izabuyela kulowo eyathengwa kuye, kulowo ilifa lensimu ebelingelakhe\x + 25.28.\x*.
\v 25 Njalo sonke isilinganiso sakho sizakuba ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele\x + 27.3.\x*; \w amagera\w** angamatshumi amabili azakuba lishekeli\x + Eks. 30.13.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Kodwa izibulo, elizelwe njengengqabutho eN\nd kosi\nd*ni elenyamazana, kakho ozalingcwelisa; loba inkabi loba imvu, ngeleN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 13.2.\x*\nd*.
\v 27 Kodwa uba lingelenyamazana engcolileyo, uzalihlenga ngokwesilinganiso sakho, engezelele phezu kwalo ingxenye yesihlanu yalo; kodwa uba lingahlengwanga, lizathengiswa ngokwesilinganiso sakho\x + 27.11,12,13.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa kakukho into eyehlukanisiweyo, umuntu ayehlukanisele iN\nd kosi\nd*, kukho konke alakho, okuvela emuntwini, loba enyamazaneni, loba okuvela ensimini yelifa lakhe, kakuyikuthengiswa, futhi kakuyikuhlengwa; konke okwehlukanisiweyo kuyingcwelengcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 27.21. Josh. 6.17,18,19.\x*.
\v 29 Yonke into eqalekisiweyo, eqalekiswe ebantwini, kayiyikuhlengwa; izabulawa lokubulawa\x + Nani 21.2,3.\x*.
\s Mayelana lokwetshumi
\p
\v 30 Lakho konke okwetshumi kwelizwe, okwenhlanyelo yelizwe, okwesithelo sezihlahla, kungokweN\nd kosi\nd*; kungcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Gen. 14.20; 28.22. Nani 18.21,24. Dute. 14.28. 2 Lan. 31.5,6,12. Neh. 13.12. Mal. 3.8,10.\x*.
\v 31 Uba umuntu ehlenga lokuhlenga kokwetshumi kwakhe, uzakwengezelela kukho ingxenye yesihlanu yakho\x + 27.13,15,19,27.\x*.
\v 32 Mayelana lakho konke okwetshumi kwezinkomo leyezimvu, konke okwedlula ngaphansi kwentonga, okwetshumi kuzakuba ngcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Hez. 20.37. Mika 7.14. Jer. 33.13.\x*.
\v 33 Kayikuhlola phakathi kokuhle lokubi, futhi kayikuntshintsha\x + 27.10.\x*. Njalo uba ekuntshintsha lokukuntshintsha, ngakho khona lokuntshintshana lakho kuzakuba ngcwele, kakuyikuhlengwa.
\p
\v 34 Leyo yimilayo iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayilaya uMozisi kubantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 26.46.\x* entabeni yeSinayi\x + 25.1; 26.46.\x*.
